rows.label: qst300202_msg0001
rows.name:
So you made it. Come on, then!
Let's get this started!

rows.label: qst300202_msg0011
rows.name: How will I answer?

rows.label: qst300202_msg0012
rows.name: Why do we have to fight?

rows.label: qst300202_msg0013
rows.name: You aren't happy with me?

rows.label: qst300202_msg0031
rows.name: Yew and Zuo told us you're strong.

rows.label: qst300202_msg0032
rows.name:
What we'd have given to fight by
Vandham's side...

rows.label: qst300202_msg0033
rows.name:
In the mercs, you've gotta prove
yourself or it doesn't mean squat!

rows.label: qst300202_msg0051
rows.name:
Nah, it's nothing personal.
Vandham respected you and
I won't contest that.

rows.label: qst300202_msg0052
rows.name:
But what made us believe in Vandham
was seeing him in action. Seeing him
at the top of his game.

rows.label: qst300202_msg0053
rows.name:
I want you to do the same. Gimme
everything you've got. Prove to me
you are what they say you are!

rows.label: qst300202_msg0071
rows.name: Let's get this show on the road!

rows.label: qst300202_msg0101
rows.name:
I surrender! Hats off to you.
That was a fine show of skill.

rows.label: qst300202_msg0102
rows.name:
But boy am I stoked after that. How
about another round? Just kidding!

rows.label: qst300202_msg0111
rows.name:
Even after we dragged you into
this brawl, you're still showing us
compassion?

rows.label: qst300202_msg0112
rows.name:
Almost feels like I'm speaking with
Vandham himself!

rows.label: qst300202_msg0113
rows.name:
He had a heart as wide as the
Cloud Sea. You two were really
alike, y'know.

rows.label: qst300202_msg0121
rows.name:
All right, I give up!
Sorry we had to do all this!

rows.label: qst300202_msg0131
rows.name:
Well, you've talked us round. But that
bloke over there's not convinced yet.

rows.label: qst300202_msg0132
rows.name:
See him? That's Jugger. You'll have to
let him take a pop at ya.
